selector.desc:
>  Since > v4.4.0 The selector button in the legend component. Currently includes both a full selection and an inverse selection. The selector button doesn't display by default, the user can manually configure it. Usage: 

    selector: [
        {
            type: 'all or inverse',
            // can be any title you like
            title: 'All'
        },
        {
            type: 'inverse',
            title: 'Inv'
        }
    ]

    // or
    selector: true

    // or
    selector: ['all', 'inverse']

